title: The Big Suey: Orlovsky Did That Once
description:
Dan pulled the 49ers helmet from the Bucket of Death. Must have been harrowing to see Jimmy Garrapolo stepping out of the back of the end zone. Does Dan Orlovsky, the guy who's famous for that play, want to continue to be famous for that play? Plus, farewell to Roger Federer.
